    public abstract class AbstractFieldPreferencePage
extends org.eclipse.jface.preference.FieldEditorPreferencePage
implements org.eclipse.ui.IWorkbenchPreferencePage
    Common parent for the most of Dr. Garbage preference pages. Notably it sets the Gr. Garbage logo as image descriptor.
